  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400 degrees.",
    "Toss the swede with olive oil, garlic, and cinnamon, and roast for 30 minutes.",
    "Let the swede cool, then puree in a blender until smooth.",
    "In a bowl, mix the pureed swede with ricotta cheese and confectioners sugar.",
    "Fill the cannoli shells with the swede mixture.",
    "Dust the tops with confectioners sugar and sprinkle with chopped pistachios.",
    "Chill in the refrigerator for at least 30 minutes before serving.",
    "Serve cold and enjoy."
